The paper discusses software design challenges and improvements for the Adapteva Epiphany architecture, which is a many-core coprocessor. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Science sub-categories of Architecture (cs.AR), Performance (cs.PF), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
